{"tid":1949932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢真實死亡數字","createTime":"2020-03-30T04:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T04:48:38.000Z","uid":245820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ec78ea69700a10f6d257c45a2b1968283d1f16","tid":1949932,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:05:01.000Z","msg":"//《美國之音》報道，中國官方預計在武漢每天發500個骨灰罈，並計劃清明節前發完。報道引述網友質疑，武漢總計8個殯儀館，若每天各館發放500個，連續12天，「不就泄露了武漢實際的死亡黑數應在4萬人以上」。 //<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中國病毒單喺武漢就令 8*500*12 = 48000人死亡</span></span><br />\n假設死亡率因為武漢醫療系統崩潰而令死亡率特別高，當係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10%</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即係大約有480000人中咗中國病毒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n計埋湖北省，甚至其他省市，肯定遠超480000人感染<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/28348/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%BC%A2%E5%8F%A3%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E9%A4%A8-%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8-28349/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E6%96%BC%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%EF%BC%9F-%E5%AE%98%E7%A8%B12535%E4%BA%BA-%E5%85%A7%E5%AA%92%E6%8F%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%AA%A8%E7%81%B0%E7%9B%92%E9%81%8B%E6%AE%AF%E5%84%80%E9%A4%A8?fbclid=IwAR2VN_PP2tNADQQBEo4yQOOajTGlUf-34aFpQcTJwfKwyDgKxolTqGHkuqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F28348%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%25AE%25AF%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8-28349%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25A8%25B12535%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%2581%25B0%25E7%259B%2592%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%25AE%